entries.femaleVariant: [Get in car]
Get the fuck out.
Rayfield's mine.
NCPD! Drop your weapons!
Hands where I can see 'em! Nice an' slow!
Jackie Welles, my old pal from the 'hood. See you haven't grown an ounce wiser.
It's a waste of effort. I have no time to testify or play at an investigation.
I suggest you toss them in the sea. Cuffed legs broken so this trash doesn't float.
Hm... Looks like this'll be a cool breeze.
Suggestin' we let 'em go, sir?
Kirk? I see the ride.
Your moment to shine, kiddo. Good luck.
Let's take this piece of wondertech for a whirl.
You're a woman of little faith.
entries.maleVariant: You're a man of little faith.

entries.femaleVariant: Now fire 'er up and call me when you're underway. Tell you where to go.
OK, easy.
What, man, never heard of thieves' honor? Finders keepers. I was first.
entries.maleVariant: What, man, never heard of thieves' honor? Finders keepers? I was first.

entries.femaleVariant: Listen, only one of two ways to do this – friendly or fucked up.
<kiroshi l="mex" o="¡¿Qué chingados...?!" t="The fuck...?" b="" a=""/>
Either way, the ending's the same – I'm takin' the car.
Same shit.
Speakin' of… your mug's familiar, too.
Yeah? Yours ain't to me.
Not familiar with yours.
How about that – a pig that chatters.
entries.maleVariant: How about that, ugh – a pig that chatters.

entries.femaleVariant: Whaddaya know – a talkative pig.
Left for Atlanta, lookin' for a slice of happiness. Guess you didn't find it.
I've always maintained it's the same for all you termites in Heywood. Born here, live here, die here.
Looks like I was right.
Hey, c'mon, Stints, give us a break, huh? You lock us up, we'll just jerk off till trial, and then what?
<mothertongue l="mex" m="el bote" b="Worst case, agh, we get some months. Hell, standin' room only nowadays in " a=", so... we'll prob'ly be out early."/>
You know fuck all about me.
You know fuck all about me.
Enough of the chatter. What now?
What now?
Truth hurts, huh? Just watch your tone – I'm not a patient man.
Gettin' booked, gonna do a stint. Heh – get it?
Are these the thieves? Ordinary street trash.
Got 'em in custody, Mr. Fujioka. We'll be takin' 'em now.
<mothertongue l="mex" m="compa" b="Nothin' personal, " a=". Just biz."/>
Hey, argh... Detective Stints! Been a while, huh?
Inspector Stints.
See? We're rich.
[Gun it]
[Hack lock] Let's give it a shot.
Get-the-fuck-out.
Wow, you can drive. Now out.
Heh, fuuuck…
C'mon, spit it out. I'm waitin'.
Rat got your tongue?
You heard 'im.
Fuck, he's here.
Stay where you are!
Don't move!
On the ground, motherfuckers! Now!
You're under arrest!
Easy now...
What the…?
Fuck!
Wha- What're you doin'?
